Problem: Add Digits
Topic: Math, Simulation
Difficulty: Easy

Approach:
Repeatedly calculate the sum of the digits of the number until it becomes a single-digit number. In each iteration, extract digits using the modulo (%) and division (/) operators, compute their sum, and update the number with this sum.

Time Complexity: O(log n)
Space Complexity: O(1)

Code:
class Solution {
public:
    int addDigits(int num) {
        while(num>9){
            int sum=0;
            while(num>0){
                sum+=num%10;
                num/=10;
            }
            num=sum;
        }
        return num;
    }
};
